<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When we return JsonModel from controller, and attach JsonStrategy with high priority, Zend\View will render layout as well.
This effect solved by JsonModel "terminal" method:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
public function testAction(){
  $result = new ViewModel\JsonModel(array(
     'success'=&gt;true,
  ));
  $result-&gt;setTerminal(true);
  return $result;
}
</code></pre>

<p>But maybe better to set $terminate property to true by default, because often JsonModel is terminator.</p>

